1.title: El regreso, sobre ruedas
1.plot: Luna and her friends are coming back from Cancún. Alfredo is organizing a big party. Ámbar reaches the villa alone, dressed in black. Sharon meets a dubious man.

2.title: Una fiesta en la mansión, sobre ruedas
2.plot: Emilia's presence worries the friends. Ámbar doubts that Luna is Sol Benson. A mysterious person sneaks through the villa. Gary announces that the runway is now owned by the Red Sharks.

3.title: Los Red Sharks, sobre ruedas
3.plot: Juliana will train the Red Sharks. Nina doesn't know what to write about. Matteo can't stop thinking about Luna. Rey visits the villa. Ámbar finds Matteo's ring.

4.title: Una propuesta de Gary, sobre ruedas
4.plot: Luna rejects Gary's offer. Rey apologizes and asks for his old job. Benicio meets Ámbar. Luna finds the ring and tells Simón that Matteo is past.

5.title: Un patinador misterioso, sobre ruedas
5.plot: Benicio succeeds in joining the Red Sharks. Ámbar doesn't trust Rey, but Luna defends him. Luna tells Nina about her feelings for Simon and Matteo hears it.

6.title: Una traición, sobre ruedas
6.plot: Luna rejects Matteo. Rey introduces the perfect maid, but she's a spy. Ámbar pushes Simón to the change. Matteo announces that his time in the Roller team is over.

7.title: ¿Matteo se va del Roller?, sobre ruedas
7.plot: Ramiro joins the Red Sharks and Yam breaks up with him. Ámbar and Rey threaten each other to tell the truth. Sharon calls Ámbar.

8.title: El regreso de Sharon, sobre ruedas
8.plot: Simón rehearses with Luna for the performance at the Open. Ámbar gets a mysterious call. Matteo doesn't want to sing with Emilia and receives another offer.

9.title: Una habitación misteriosa, sobre ruedas
9.plot: Luna has a nightmare related to Sharon's room. The guys from the Roller Band want Matteo to sing with them. Luna is afraid that Simón doesn't feel the way she does.

10.title: Una confusión de sentimientos, sobre ruedas
10.plot: Nina gets an unexpected visit. Luna comes close Simón. Eric says the rose is not his. Matteo wants to make Luna forget Simón. Simón tells Luna what he feels.

11.title: El fin de Gastina, sobre ruedas
11.plot: Luna is hurt by Simón's confession. Alfredo gives Rey the oversight of his finances. Ámbar wants to use Simón to harm his friends.

12.title: Un espía, sobre ruedas
12.plot: Luna asks Nina to record a video. Rey suspects Maggie. Matteo asks Luna if she's in love with Simón and Simón hears it by accident.

13.title: Un entrenamiento secreto, sobre ruedas
13.plot: Ana helps Alfredo with legal issues. Sharon has a plan. Luna will perform with Matteo in the video. Someone films the training in the Roller.

14.title: Encerrados, sobre ruedas
14.plot: Luna has a disturbing dream. Rey follows Maggie. Benicio deceives Jazmín and finds out something. Emilia has a great idea how to stop the others from shooting the video.

15.title: Un videoclip borrado, sobre ruedas
15.plot: In search of the truth, Rey confronted Sharon. Ámbar and Emilia are again causing problems for the Roller team. Matteo and Luna get very close.

16.title: Un vídeo revelador, sobre ruedas
16.plot: Luna rejects Matteo's approach. The video is on the internet. Nina wants to help Eric. Jim and Yam are happy. Ramiro makes a big mistake.

17.title: Gary descubre la verdad, sobre ruedas
17.plot: Maggie and Rey make a radical decision regarding Sharon. Matteo finds out that Simón is interested in Ámbar. Gary sees the video and takes drastic consequences.

18.title: El despido de Juliana, sobre ruedas
18.plot: Gary's decisions are on everyone's mind. Maggie and Rey are setting up a plan. Gary will coach the Red Sharks. Simón comes close to Ámbar as well as Matteo and Luna approach.

19.title: Un abrazo, sobre ruedas
19.plot: Emilia plans to bring Matteo and Luna apart. Sharon reveals her revenge plan. Matteo solves Nico's, Pedro's and Simón's problem. Ámbar happens to overhear a conversation between Nina and Luna.

20.title: Un duelo, sobre ruedas
20.plot: The boys accept Matteo's proposal to move to the loft together. Gary and Ana are kissing for the first time. Emilia kisses Matteo and films it. Luna admits she still likes Matteo.

21.title: Una falsa relación, sobre ruedas
21.plot: Emilia tries to show Luna a picture where she kisses Matteo. Jazmín films Ámbar and Benicio as they kiss. Ámbar threatens Rey and Maggie to tell Valentes everything.

22.title: Invitadas especiales, sobre ruedas
22.plot: Gary hires Juliana. Matteo asks Emilia to erase the photo of her kiss. Nina can't forget Gastón. Sharon has changed her appearance and Ámbar is surprised.

23.title: Los preparativos del Open Music, sobre ruedas
23.plot: Juliana accuses Gary of subsequently changing the contract and gets help from Ana. The Open takes place in the villa. Rey and Maggie try to steal a painting from the villa.

24.title: Un cuadro, sobre ruedas
24.plot: Luna and Nina catch Rey and Maggie exchanging a picture. Luna proposes a slumber party. Juliana is dissatisfied with the performance of the Red Sharks. Luna makes an unexpected confession.

25.title: Un Open Music en la mansión, sobre ruedas (Parte 1)
25.plot: Luna admits she still loves Matteo. Ana asks the wrong Gary why he wears headphones. Luna and Matteo come close and sing together.

26.title: Un Open Music en la mansión, sobre ruedas (Parte 2)
26.plot: Luna is devastated after Open Music. Nina and Delfina try to find out how the photo between Matteo and Emilia came about.

27.title: Un cuadro desaparecido, sobre ruedas
27.plot: Luna is determined to forget Matteo. Emilia gives Matteo the choice: either he does her a favor and she will help with Luna or she will complicate it. Alfredo has brought forward the auction, which puts Rey and Maggie under pressure.

28.title: Una subasta en la mansión, sobre ruedas
28.plot: A team of journalists and an internet star come to interview the Red Sharks. Emilia has managed to convince Matteo that they meet secretly so that Ámbar sees them together. Both fake paintings are sold at auction.

29.title: Red Sharks Festival, sobre ruedas (Parte 1)
29.plot: Luna learns that Matteo wants to meet Emilia secretly. Double punishment for Matteo: Luna doesn't want to talk to him anymore and Emilia refuses him the proof video that he is innocent.

30.title: Red Sharks Festival, sobre ruedas (Parte 2)
30.plot: Since they were denied access to the Red Sharks Festival, the Roller team skates before the Jam and Roller. Nina films them and the video is a sensation. The audience that wanted to see the Red Sharks comes to see the Roller team.

31.title: El accidente de Matteo, sobre ruedas
31.plot: Luna is very worried because Matteo doesn't recognize her. Ada explains to Ana about the true identity of Gary. Ámbar, Benicio, Emilia and Ramiro are waiting for the thunderstorm of Gary, after the flop at the Red Shark Festival.

32.title: Un arresto, sobre ruedas
32.plot: Because Mónica, Miguel and Alfredo are arrested, Luna is very worried. She is shocked when she sees Sharon in a car, but Sharon drives away quickly. Gary wants to talk to Ana, but she refuses.

33.title: Amnesia, sobre ruedas
33.plot: Luna and her family puzzle who has faked the pictures. Rey and Ámbar are worried about the conversation. Juliana is pleased about her termination.

34.title: ¿Adiós Red Sharks?, sobre ruedas
34.plot: Luna discovers a photo of Bernie in Sharon's room. The Red Sharks are stunned by Gary's decision. Matteo refuses to continue playing with the band. Mónica tries to convince Ámbar of her solidarity.

35.title: Una propuesta complicada, sobre ruedas
35.plot: The Roller team is shocked by Gary's proposal. Ámbar and Benicio are working together to achieve their goal. Ana, the Valentes and Alfredo are convinced that Sharon is behind the whole thing.

36.title: Una nueva casa para la Roller Band, sobre ruedas
36.plot: Luna is very worried when she learns that Alfredo has big gambling debts in the casino. The boys are at a loss after Gary throws them out of the loft. Rey tells Sharon that Luna found the papers in Sharon's room.

37.title: Bienvenido Michel, sobre ruedas
37.plot: Luna thought that exchange student Michel was a girl. Pedro and Simón are impressed by Nico's decision to go. Ana confesses to Nina what Gary López is all about. Ramiro mourns his bursting dreams, but Eric gives him new courage.

38.title: Un sospechoso, sobre ruedas
38.plot: The friends are sad because Nico leaves, but Luna manages to cheer everyone up again. At the party Michel is dancing with Luna. Alfredo almost discovers Sharon with Rey, but Maggie distracts him.

39.title: Una nueva responsable del Roller, sobre ruedas
39.plot: Everyone in the Roller is shocked by Ámbar's appointment as Managing Director. Rey sows mistrust between the Valentes and Alfredo. Nina tells Michel about the special connection between Luna and Matteo.

40.title: Un Flash-Open Music, sobre ruedas
40.plot: Luna tries to convince Matteo not to give up singing, but he does not want to hear about it anymore. Simón finds out that Ámbar changed Felipe's phone number. She promises to apologize to Luna for that.

41.title: ¿Un nuevo amor?, sobre ruedas
41.plot: Luna and Michel are very close. Jazmín surprisingly joins in and asks if they are a couple. Ramiro is very happy about his performance with his friends. Ámbar is in trouble at work.

42.title: Un falso numero de teléfono, sobre ruedas
42.plot: Luna is angry at Simón because he didn't tell her that the number of Felipe Mendevilla was reversed. Rey makes a plan to deceive Alfredo. Matteo is still convinced that Luna is not interested in him and would be happier without him.

43.title: Una falsa identidad, sobre ruedas
43.plot: Luna meets Felipe Mendevilla, who makes her a suggestion. Matteo wants to get help from Luna. Simón and Benicio argue about Ámbar. Eric decides to overcome his fear and talk to Nina.

44.title: La nueva identidad de Sharon, sobre ruedas
44.plot: Emilia and Benicio want to stop Ramiro from going back to the Roller Team, but his decision is certain. Nina tells Eric that he's just a good friend for her. Luna tells Mónica about the red-haired woman she saw in the garden.

45.title: ¿Matteo o Michel?, sobre ruedas
45.plot: Luna finds the key to the chest, but before she can try it, she is stopped by Nina's message. Rey warns Sharon. Benicio is jealous of Simón and makes Ámbar a scene. Matteo is still sad, but Luna plans to build him up with a video shoot.

46.title: Amores confundidos, sobre ruedas
46.plot: Luna doesn't know what to say to Michel. Ámbar tells Simón that she has left Benicio. Juliana comes back to work as a trainer again. Delfi shows the team the final cut music video of Matteo. Rey steals the key from Maggie.

47.title: Un beso inesperado, sobre ruedas
47.plot: Matteo has watched the kiss between Luna and Michel. Rey picks up the key for the chest from Maggie's bag. Emma notes that Simón doesn't want anything from her. Simón tells Ámbar how much he misses Mexico, and she has an idea.

48.title: La competencia se acerca, sobre ruedas
48.plot: Matteo is pleased with the interest of the music producer. Luna and he come closer again. Benicio and Emilia suggest Ámbar to skate as a group for the film-casting, but Ámbar refuses. Luna is confused by her feelings.

49.title: Una elección, sobre ruedas
49.plot: The Roller-Team convinces Juliana. Maggie almost tells Mónica the truth. Benicio informs Ámbar that she has to inform Vidia that the Roller-Team is using the track. Juliana wants Luna and Matteo to dance as a couple.

50.title: Una fiesta mexicana, sobre ruedas
50.plot: Matteo thinks that Michel gave the bracelet to Luna. Pedro tells him to fight for Luna. Alfredo asks Mónica to build an altar for Lili and Bernie for the Day of the Dead. Sharon uses Rey's help to get into the mansion.

51.title: Una duda, sobre ruedas
51.plot: Matteo's appearance is successful. Luna is impressed and she is asked if Lutteo is back. Ámbar is mad at Benicio because of the kiss. But Simón is mad at her and tells her that he should not have trusted her.

52.title: Un anillo perdido, sobre ruedas
52.plot: Luna tries to talk to Matteo, but they are interrupted by Michel. The ring falls down and Matteo thinks that this is a sign that they should not be together. Michel tells Luna that he has the opportunity to go to Rome.

53.title: Ámbar regresa al equípo, sobre ruedas
53.plot: Luna tells Michel that she only sees him as a friend. Michel accepts that and decides to go to Rome. Simón asks Ámbar to forgive him. Yam goes to the singing exam, but overlaps with the group casting.

54.title: Un cómplice, sobre ruedas
54.plot: Ámbar and Luna find Rey with the stolen pictures and tell Alfredo and Valentes, but Rey escapes. Sharon treats Rey badly. Jazmín almost erases the video of Maggie and Rey stealing the picture.

55.title: Los secretos empiezan a revelarse, sobre ruedas
55.plot: Matteo tries to talk to Luna. Jazmín shows Luna the video in which Maggie and Rey steal the pictures. Luna informs her parents and Ana asks Maggie for help in finding Sharon. Simón assures Ámbar that he will support her.

56.title: Un nuevo paso, sobre ruedas
56.plot: Luna and Matteo kiss in the rain. Police want to arrest Sharon, but she is not there. Simón has a romantic surprise for Ámbar and they kiss. Luna informs her friends that Lutteo is back.

57.title: Una noticia, sobre ruedas
57.plot: Luna thinks she saw Sharon. Rey wants to go to the police to make up for his mistake and find Sharon. Everyone is afraid Sharon might hurt them. Sharon calls Ámbar to ask for help finding the key to the chest.

58.title: Una idea, sobre ruedas
58.plot: Juliana informs the Roller Team that they have booked for the opening of a festival. Emilia and Benicio steal important documents for the Roller and inform Vidia about it. Eric and Nina are happy about their kiss and are planning a date.

59.title: Un incendio, sobre ruedas
59.plot: Luna is worried. She feels that something strange could happen. Matteo asks Simón and Pedro to sing a song together on his album. Nina agrees to a relationship with Eric. Ámbar joins the Roller Team.

60.title: Patinamos por una última vez
60.plot: Luna dreams that she closes the chest and wakes up next to it. She finally understands why Sharon hated her and forgives her. Ámbar visits Sharon in the hospital and Sharon shows honest regret.

1.title: ¿Un sueño o una pesadilla?, sobre ruedas
1.plot: Luna is overwhelmed when she finds a medallion that she had already dreamed of. At the same time, Luna worries about Matteo, because he has completely disappeared from the scene. Will he come back?

2.title: Un sol y una luna, sobre ruedas
2.plot: Luna is becoming more and more popular, but Ámbar doesn't want to accept it and forges a plan to regain its popularity. Finally, Matteo comes back, but he has to bring Luna bad news.

3.title: Una actitud sospechosa, sobre ruedas
3.plot: Luna can finally address Matteo, but doubts about Matteo's honesty. Finally, she pours out her heart to Simón, who wants to direct her thoughts to the next Open, and wants to kindle her fighting spirit.

4.title: ¡Atrapada por la cámara!, sobre ruedas
4.plot: Luna doesn't get rid of the feeling that Matteo hid something from her, but she can not penetrate him. Meanwhile, the tension on the next Open is rising, because Luna is not the only one whose head is occupied with other things.

5.title: El primer Open Music del año, sobre ruedas
5.plot: Ámbar feels threatened, as her popularity continues to wane from day to day, whereupon she forges a bad plan. In the meantime, Luna's doubts about her true identity grow until Sharon and Rey make an all-changing discovery.

6.title: ¡Luna es Sol Benson!, sobre ruedas
6.plot: Luna tries to fathom her past and wants to find out where the ominous sun medallion comes from. When Sharon finds out who Sol Benson really is, she forges a plan with Rey to prevent Luna from experiencing the truth.

7.title: Una nueva competencia, sobre ruedas
7.plot: A new Rollerskate contest is coming and Luna is trying to get a dance troupe up, but Ámbar is trying to spoil her all the members. Sharon's anger at Luna leads to a mistake that could turn her into disaster.

8.title: Una plan contra Luna, sobre ruedas
8.plot: Sharon loses her mind about what she has found out about Luna, while Nico is annoyed by Jim's trust break. Matteo is now running for the 'Adrenalines', which leads to problems with Luna. And soon there is still a costume party.

9.title: Una cámara rota, sobre ruedas
9.plot: Luna and Nina are on the verge of solving the puzzle around their medallion, Matteo helps Luna to a great choreography and Simón persuades Jazmín to take the last place in Luna's team. In the meantime, Sharon deliberates to dismiss the Valentes.

10.title: Una fiesta de disfraces, sobre ruedas
10.plot: Lunas and Nina's costumes for the upcoming competition are gone. At the last minute Mora sews costumes of plastic waste, which are very enthusiastic. In the meantime Ámbar prepares for the last step of her devilish plan.

11.title: Un incendio en la pista, sobre ruedas
11.plot: After the power failure on the train, all the things that could have happened are puzzling. Matteo, however, faces a bigger problem: he must separate from Luna before the feelings become too strong.

12.title: Secretos del pasado, sobre ruedas
12.plot: Santi Owen tells the kids that the Roller is to be closed, which the kids do not want to accept without fighting. In the meantime Matteo has to nibble in a fight with himself, because he has to finally talk to Luna about her relationship.

13.title: Una ilusión, sobre ruedas
13.plot: With the knowledge that Matteo is together with Fer, Luna addresses him and wants clarity about their relationship, but doesn't get the desired answer. In the meantime, Sharon has doubts about Ámbar's stay abroad and forging a plan.

14.title: Una ayuda, sobre ruedas
14.plot: Ámbar has a lot to do with Sharon's supposed revelation and seeks help with her girlfriends. Meanwhile, Luna persuades her friends to organize an event to collect money for the repair of the skate track.

15.title: Un plan para el Roller, sobre ruedas
15.plot: The kids have a plan to make the skating run as good as possible. While Luna and Nina are still trying to figure out the truth about Luna's past, Fer and Matteo are getting closer and closer.

16.title: ¿Ámbar es Sol Benson?, sobre ruedas
16.plot: Sharon tells everyone that Ámbar is her niece Sol Benson, where both Ámbar and Luna have a lot to bite. In addition, Pedros decision to sing only the best in the Roller makes for discord and tension within the group.

17.title: ¿El Roller va a cerrar?, sobre ruedas
17.plot: Still shocked by the announced closure of the Roller, Jim, Yam and Nico give everything to make the last Open an unforgettable event. Meanwhile, Luna is close to Ámbar and is the reason for Matteo's behavior on the track.

18.title: Las esperanzas se rompen, sobre ruedas
18.plot: Alfredo continues to ask questions about Ámbar's past while Sharon denied Rey to destroy any evidence of Sol Benson's past. Amanda continues to hold on to her assertion of having a firm friend.

19.title: Una nueva esperanza, sobre ruedas
19.plot: With combined forces, the kids give everything they need to repair the broken pipe. Luna finally finds out more about the recently found photo, while her family support Simón, Jim and Yam by all means.

20.title: Adiós Roller, sobre ruedas
20.plot: Ana tells Rosales that Ricardo has installed cameras in the Roller. Rosales wants to close the Roller immediately, so the children prefer the Open. Ricardo convinces the CEO Vidias to look at his new camera system.

21.title: ¿Descubren la verdad?, sobre ruedas
21.plot: After Matteo learns about the closure of the Roller, he does his best to help his friends from the Roller, but Fer feels as if he's gone. Ricardo and Ana, on the other hand, come a little closer.

22.title: El Roller no se cerrará, sobre ruedas
22.plot: A great surprise is the course for great joy: The Jam and Roller is to be reopened. Ámbar, however, already has her next plan with Delfi and asks Jazmín to spy on her team.

23.title: Celos, sobre ruedas
23.plot: Ana wants to confess Mora against the will of Ricardo from her kiss. Sebastián and Luna get closer. Gaston believes he has to decide between studying and Nina, while Alfredo makes contact with his youth love.

24.title: Una nueva entrenadora, sobre ruedas
24.plot: Juliana, the new manager of the Jam and Roller, is not particularly enthusiastic about the gait. While Ámbar blackmail Matteo to shoot a video with her, Luna follows with Nina a new track, which is to throw light on the mystery around the medal.

25.title: La grabación de la coreografía, sobre ruedas
25.plot: Despite successful rehearsals, Juliana continues to exert pressure. Matteo, however, is under even greater pressure because he has to choose between his father and his friends. Amanda is getting nervous. Will she open the secret?

26.title: Lagrimas y disculpas, sobre ruedas
26.plot: Matteo must find a way to deal with the consequences of his decision and Ámbars extortion attempts. Meanwhile, a melody at Luna makes a very strange reaction and Juliana continues to exert pressure on the gang.

27.title: Una disculpa, sobre ruedas
27.plot: Ámbar and Matteo realize that the video with which they wanted to make fun of Luna and Sebastián, also for them doesn't have without consequences. Meanwhile, Sharon and Rey try to get rid of Alfredo, but this one is already a step ahead.

28.title: ¿Un nuevo amor?, sobre ruedas
28.plot: Luna and Nina are looking for more clues to help solve the mystery around the medal, while Pedro continues to focus on Eve's attention. And again, Juliana is making a drastic decision for disgust.

29.title: Matteo se va de los adrenaline, sobre ruedas
29.plot: Luna, Nina, Tino and Cato go to the pizzeria where the planned meeting is to take place. It is, however, a very different discovery, which Luna lingers the language. Ámbar still tries to put Matteo under pressure - in vain.

30.title: Mentiras, sobre ruedas
30.plot: Luna makes another effort to meet her informer. With Delfi's help, Ámbar finally manages to convey the truth about Matteo to Luna. Alfredo's camouflage begins to crumble as Miguel comes behind his secret.

31.title: Una pelea, sobre ruedas
31.plot: Luna can not forgive Matteo easy. In addition, Ámbar smashes salt into the wound, making fun of Matteo. In the meantime, Mónica also learns about Alfredo's secret and is angry with Miguel for not telling her about it.

32.title: ¿Matteo quiere volver con Luna?, sobre ruedas
32.plot: Juliana throws Luna out of the Roller-team. Mora does not want to marry Ricardo. Nina finds out that Tino and Cato hide behind "Ticanoto". Matteo wants to tell Luna that he loves her, but learns that she is with Sebastián.

33.title: Un mensaje, sobre ruedas
33.plot: Shortly before the competition Juliana fires the entire team, which is a step closer to the goal of her plan. When Alfredo still assumed that Sol Benson's photo had fallen victim to the washing machine, Rey had already found the photo.

34.title: Quiero volver al equipo, sobre ruedas
34.plot: No chance to enter the competition remains unfulfilled: while Simón turns to Vidia, the gang turns to the public. Meanwhile, Luna tries to get information from Cato about the medallion.

35.title: La verdad está cerca, sobre ruedas
35.plot: Still without support, the team has not yet given up hope and continues to train bitterly. Juliana, however, is pursuing another plan. Rey looks like obsessed with Luna's medallion and finally even lunches Lunas things.

36.title: El regreso del equipo del Roller, sobre ruedas
36.plot: Finally, the social media campaign is bearing fruit because according to the vote Juliana is to work again with the gang. However, Juliana can't stop putting a spoke in their wheel. Meanwhile, Nina tries to come clean with Gastón.

37.title: Una nueva pareja, sobre ruedas
37.plot: There will only be one main contestant at the competition. Luna has to skate with Matteo. Jazmín guesses that Eva has a twin sister. Gastón doesn't forgive Nina for having lied to him. Matteo tells his father that he wants to become a musician.

38.title: ¿Quién se va?, sobre ruedas
38.plot: Simón is unintentionally involved in an argument between Pedro and Nico. This is about Eva, who has her own problems, because her well-kept secret is in danger. Meanwhile Juliana refuses to follow the wishes of the gang.

39.title: Una declaración amorosa, sobre ruedas
39.plot: Fer finally comes clean with Matteo. While Matteo asks Ramiro to join the Roller team again, Ámbar urges Delfi to leave the same. Luna and Mónica are completely dissolved when they realize that Luna's medallion has disappeared.

40.title: Un accidente, sobre ruedas (Parte 1)
40.plot: There is rebellion in the Roller Team: Matteo asks Ramiro to return, while Ámbar Delfi is putting pressure on the team to leave the team. Luna and Mónica are desperate as they realize that Luna's medal has disappeared.

41.title: Un accidente, sobre ruedas (Parte 2)
41.plot: Luna has to face her fears and learn to trust herself. Matteo, on the other hand, is ready to give up everything for her. But will she take him back?

42.title: Una medallita, sobre ruedas
42.plot: The dispute of the Roller Band seems so fixed that there is no way to find each other again. Especially Pedro and Simon have trouble communicating with each other. Luna, on the other hand, could not be happier.

43.title: Más cerca de la verdad, sobre ruedas
43.plot: Luna and Nina discover the scarf of Señora Rodriguez at Rey. Juliana decided to re-position the team and gave the group a task that everyone had to prove.

44.title: Una carta, sobre ruedas
44.plot: Lunas and Matteo's love lasts, but Ámbar has a plan to cross the happiness of the young couple. In addition, Luna has to decide, shortly before the big Open, whether to support her boyfriend or her friends.

45.title: Un Open Music de oportunidad, sobre ruedas (Parte 1)
45.plot: Mora has arranged a double date for herself and Ana, but regret it quickly. Alfredo has doubts about traveling with Rosa, which Sharon doesn't like. Will her plan to get Alfredo out of the house at last fail?

46.title: Un Open Music de oportunidad, sobre ruedas (Parte 2)
46.plot: Jazmín makes up Ámbar ready for the competition, but the result leaves something to be desired. For Ámbar it is clear that this is sabotage. Meanwhile, Luna is still trying to find out more about her past.

47.title: Las votaciones del concurso, sobre ruedas
47.plot: Alfredo overheard a conversation between Rey and Silvana, which arouses his mistrust. Meanwhile, Jazmín hopes to have a pressure against Ámbar with which she can Ámbar keep away from Simón.

48.title: La lucha por Simón, sobre ruedas
48.plot: Luna is annoyed because Matteo plans his career without Simón. In addition, she has to cope with the fact that Alfredo will make a long journey. A change in the candidate selection at the upcoming Solo-Open generate a big surprise.

49.title: ¿Mi novio o mi mejor amigo?, sobre ruedas
49.plot: Vidias contest is imminent. Luna is faced with the decision to support either her best friend or her boyfriend. Meanwhile, Ámbar is still pursuing her plan and creating tensions between Luna and Matteo.

50.title: La fiesta de gala, sobre ruedas (Parte 1)
50.plot: Finally, the two finalists will be announced. When Nina introduces Gastón and Xavi to each other, Gastón becomes jealous and reacts irritably to Xavi's arrogant style. Mónica hears a conversation with Rosa, which left her speechless.

61.title: Secretos de la família Benson, sobre ruedas
61.plot: The Roller's team qualifies for the final. Luna celebrates, but her joy is short-lived. As her investigation progresses, things start to get complicated with Matteo.

62.title: El fin de Lutteo, sobre ruedas
62.plot: Luna and Matteo argue. Juliana discovers a truth that leaves her breathless.

63.title: Un culpable, sobre ruedas
63.plot: Luna and Matteo feel the weight of separation. No one suspects who Benicio's accomplice is, but they set out to investigate. Juliana leaves the Roller, but Luna has an idea to convince her to stay.

64.title: Una investigación, sobre ruedas
64.plot: Luna has an idea to convince Juliana to stay in the Roller. With the help of Nina and Simón, Luna tries to continue the investigation of her past, but finds herself with a difficult obstacle to overcome.

65.title: Una propuesta especial, sobre ruedas
65.plot: Luna dreams with her past. Everyone prepares a big surprise for Juliana.

66.title: Matteo celoso, sobre ruedas
66.plot: Luna and her friends convince Juliana. The investigation of her past advances and haunting clues come to light.

67.title: ¿Algo más que amigos?, sobre ruedas
67.plot: Luna is willing to do everything to discover her truth, but the adventure takes her too far. Matteo sees something that makes him furious, Luna discovers something about Ámbar and Simón that leaves her speechless.

68.title: Mensaje oculto, sobre ruedas
68.plot: A revealing truth is discovered by Luna.

69.title: Cerca de la verdad, sobre ruedas
69.plot: Destiny prepares great surprises and revelations for Luna. Everyone gets some shocking news.

70.title: ¿Mi verdadera identidad?, sobre ruedas
70.plot: Luna discovers that Ámbar is not Sol Benson. All the secrets begin to lose strength, but she can not see the truth clearly. Luna and Matteo want to distance themselves, but it seems impossible.

71.title: ¿Dónde está Sol Benson?, sobre ruedas
71.plot: Luna discovers that Ámbar is not Sol Benson. All the secrets begin to lose strength, but she can not see the truth clearly. Luna and Matteo want to distance themselves, but it seems something impossible.

72.title: Esperando una respuesta, sobre ruedas
72.plot: Luna kisses Matteo. Mysterious things continue to happen in the mansion , but some masks begin to fall for the truth to be revealed. Ámbar generates great impact.

73.title: Ámbar es descubierta, sobre ruedas
73.plot: Everyone discovers that Ámbar is responsible for the fire. Luna tries to get closer to Matteo, but gets a hard answer.

74.title: Un momento de confesiones, sobre ruedas
74.plot: Luna is disappointed with Matteo, but one step closer to the truth. The team prepares for the Rodafest, but Ámbar plans a terrible revenge.

75.title: Mucho más que un sueño, sobre ruedas
75.plot: Sharon tries to hide what Alfredo finds out, while Luna has an important dream. A devastating revaluation is approaching.

76.title: Espionaje, trampas y más problemas, sobre ruedas
76.plot: Monica, Miguel and Ámbar travel to Cancun. Luna has nightmares that give her a clue to the past. Simon has problems writing the lyrics for the contest. The team has to rehearse a new heavy lift figure.

77.title: Un secreto no tan secreto, sobre ruedas
77.plot: Luna does not believe in a reconciliation with Matteo. The Roller team worries because the competition knows their secret choreography. Alfredo tries everything to contact the Valentes while he is in the sanatorium.

78.title: Un viaje a Cancún, sobre ruedas
78.plot: Cancun hosts the finale of the "Roda Fest". Nobody knows the new team member at the "Sliders", but Simon and Luna have a suspicion. Alfredo unexpectedly gets escape help from Rey. Cato wants to make a proposal to Amanda.

79.title: La final de la Rodafest en México, sobre ruedas (Parte 1)
79.plot: Ámbar is now in the team of "Sliders" and steals the skates of Luna to prevent them from starting. Sharon is afraid of Alfredo after Rey has told him the whole truth. The decisive competition of the two scooter teams begins.

80.title: La final de la Rodafest en México, sobre ruedas (Parte 2)
80.plot: The finale of the "Roda Fest" is decided by the "Sliders". But at the award ceremony there is a surprise. Alfredo tells Luna the truth about her origins. Sharon flees and leaves Ámbar back. She wants to take revenge on Luna.

imdb.plot outline: Luna Valente lives with her family in Cancún, Mexico. She goes to school, has her own group of friends, has a job, and loves to skate. However, her life changes when her parents are given a job offer that moves them to Buenos Aires, Argentina. There she finds a skating rink named Jam and Roller where she learns free styling. She makes new friends and falls in love with Matteo Balsano.

plot: Luna Valente lives with her family in Cancún, Mexico. She goes to school, has her own group of friends, has a job, and loves to skate. However, her life changes when her parents are given a job offer that moves them to Buenos Aires, Argentina. There she finds a skating rink named Jam and Roller where she learns free styling.
